snippet.title: DuckTales Adventure Map
snippet.description: Discover treasure and trouble at every turn in the DuckTales Adventure Map! From McDuck Manor to Mount Neverrest, zoom from adventure to legendary puzzles in the Sunchaser, and deposit your riches at The Money Bin! Solve a mystery or rewrite history as Huey, Dewey, Louie, Webby, and other Duckburg citizens. Life is like a hurricane in the DuckTales Adventure Map! WOO-OO!
